    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Don't Play This</strong> 》是一款步行模拟器类型的第一人称独立恐怖游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319120/extras/2d1fad337baf5f7f62d9777549ca022a.avif?t=1771063380\" width=640 height=82 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏简介</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319120/extras/1db574fef06012c6ce4da2bd07f123a5.poster.avif?t=1771063380\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319120/extras/1db574fef06012c6ce4da2bd07f123a5.webm?t=1771063380\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319120/extras/1db574fef06012c6ce4da2bd07f123a5.mp4?t=1771063380\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 人们经常用相机录下一些视频，但这些视频却成为了他们最后的记忆。 你必须重温这些时刻，体验是什么永远切断了录像。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏玩法</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319120/extras/a917ab07edd8ab45d54a57dbd9c50393.poster.avif?t=1771063380\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319120/extras/a917ab07edd8ab45d54a57dbd9c50393.webm?t=1771063380\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319120/extras/a917ab07edd8ab45d54a57dbd9c50393.mp4?t=1771063380\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将穿越几个不同的地点，不断遭遇居住在其中的恐怖生物。精美的画面和高品质的 3D 音效将帮助您充分体验游戏的氛围。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - 步行模拟器；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - 第一人称视角；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - 多种视觉风格；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - 逼真的画面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >注意事项 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中的闪光可能导致癫痫发作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
